title: Railworks TS2014 SSS SDJR 7F Enhancement Pack
description:
A comprehensive reworking of the old and dated 7F locomotive adding many exciting new features

Breathe New Life Into the Somerset and Dorset Railway's Finest Stalwarts

A comprehensive reworking of the old and dated 7F locomotive adding many exciting new features including:
- An authentic and advanced sound set
- A set of repaints. Includes EVERY livery ever carried by the class - we believe! As well as two preservation era liveries
- Full reworking of steam particle effects
- More realistic performance
- Authentic scenario's for the S&D and two special ones for the Settle and Carlisle line



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.




A Team tpb_4_ever upload.
